sec.p:
The interactions between lysAB-vT2 or lysAB-vT2-fusion with three antibiotics (imipenem, colistin and polymyxin B), three disinfectants (quaternary ammonium compound (QACs), Chloroxylenol, Sodium Hypochlorite), two heavy metals (CuCl2, ZnCl2) and bacteriophage vPhT2 were screened by growth inhibition assay at 0.25 × the MIC of two agents. The host for testing of all agents was ATCC 19606. A. baumannii AB329 was used for testing bacteriophage. The percent inhibition was calculated as the formular below\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
